OL,3,CConvicted drug dealer spared jail in
OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FA Guernsey man with a long history of
OL,7,Foffending has avoided prison in what
OL,8,Fis being described as an "exceptional"
OL,9,Fdecision by the island's Royal Court.
OL,11,FWesley Guilbert, 45, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fsix counts relating to possession and
OL,13,Fsupply of Class A and B drugs.
OL,15,FThe court heard how officers executed
OL,16,Fa search warrant at his house at the
OL,17,Fend of June 2023.
