OL,3,CConvicted drug dealer spared jail in
OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FThey found 21.11 grams of MDMA and
OL,7,F1.44 grams of morphine, both Class A
OL,8,Fdrugs, together with 8.5 grams of the
OL,9,FClass B drug cannabis resin and a
OL,10,Fquantity of medicinal cannabis.
OL,12,FThe collective street value of all of
OL,13,Fthe drugs recovered was said to be
OL,14,Fmore than #4,500.
OL,16,FGuilbert was said to have been
OL,17,Fcooperative throughout and told
OL,18,Fofficers that the cannabis and MDMA,
OL,19,Fotherwise known as ecstasy, were for
OL,20,Fhis personal use.
