OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FMore than #800 in cash, together with
OL,7,Fdigital scales were also recovered,
OL,8,Fwhile analysis of Guilbert's mobile
OL,9,Fphone revealed evidence relating to
OL,10,Fthe supply of seven ecstasy tablets
OL,11,Ffor a total of #140.
OL,13,FIn sentencing, Judge Catherine Fooks
OL,14,Fnoted that Guilbert was no stranger to
OL,15,Fthe Royal Court and had a long list of
OL,16,Fprevious convictions including
OL,17,Fburglary, robbery and grievous bodily
OL,18,Fharm.
