OL,3,CConvicted drug dealer spared jail in
OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FHe was handed a nine-year sentence in
OL,7,F2014 for drug offences, including the
OL,8,Fproduction of crystal
OL,9,Fmethylamphetamine.
OL,11,FHowever, Judge Fooks said she had been
OL,12,Fstruck by letters from his family and
OL,13,Ffriends, together with evidence that
OL,14,Fhe had turned his life around.
OL,16,FHe was given a two-year prison
OL,17,Fsentence suspended for three years,
OL,18,Ftogether with a probation order for
OL,19,Fthree years.
