OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FAn order was also made to destroy the
OL,7,Fdrugs.
OL,9,FDuring that time, Guilbert will have
OL,10,Fto undergo drug testing and take part
OL,11,Fin a rehabilitation programme.
OL,13,FJudge Fooks warned him that not
OL,14,Fcomplying with any of the conditions
OL,15,Fcould lead to the decision being
OL,16,Frevoked and re-sentencing applied.
OL,18,FShe added that she could not emphasise
OL,19,Fjust how "exceptional" this was.
