OL,3,CConvicted drug dealer spared jail in
OL,4,C'exceptional' court decision
OL,6,FJudge Fooks explained: "You promised
OL,7,Fthat you would agree to any conditions
OL,8,Fand any order, were the court willing
OL,9,Fto give you a chance. You said would
OL,10,Fgrasp it with both hands."
OL,12,FShe said that this was Guilbert's
OL,13,Fchance to turn his back on his 30-year
OL,14,Fpast but her words came with a note of
OL,15,Fcaution.
OL,17,FJudge Fooks said: "If you come back,
OL,18,Fyou can expect to spend a long time in
OL,19,Fprison. Take this chance for the sake
OL,20,Fof your family and the community, do
OL,21,Fnot let them or yourself down."
